            <title>[OPENJPA-374] OpenJPA build process enhances Entity classes even when testing is deactivated via -Dtest=false</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-374</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;$ mvn package -Dtest=false&lt;br/&gt;
attempts to enhance all the known Entity classes.&lt;br/&gt;
It should not. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
